* Sub class BlueCollar_Employee
*******************************************************
CLASS BLUECOLLAR_EMPLOYEE DEFINITION
           INHERITING FROM EMPLOYEE.
  PUBLIC SECTION.
    METHODS LIF_EMPLOYEE~SET_ATTRIBUTES REDEFINITION.
ENDCLASS.

*---- CLASS BlueCollar_Employee IMPLEMENTATION
CLASS BLUECOLLAR_EMPLOYEE IMPLEMENTATION.
  METHOD LIF_EMPLOYEE~SET_ATTRIBUTES.
    CALL METHOD SUPER->LIF_EMPLOYEE~SET_ATTRIBUTES
      EXPORTING
        IM_EMPLOYEE_NO   = IM_EMPLOYEE_NO
        IM_EMPLOYEE_NAME = IM_EMPLOYEE_NAME
        IM_WAGE          = IM_WAGE.
  ENDMETHOD.
ENDCLASS.

